ISTANBUL Liverpool are the Uefa Super Cup champions after edging Chelsea 5-4 on post match penalties in Istanbul. Both sides had battled to a 1-1 draw in regulation time and there was no separating them even after extra time after Sadio Mane and Jorginho scored for a 2-2 stalemate. Chelsea striker Tammy Abraham saw his penalty stopped by Adrian's outstretched leg to hand Liverpool the trophy.  